snippet.title: Octopus City Blues - Teaser
snippet.description:
Enter Octopus City, humanity's last bastion in a frozen world. Meet Kaf, a tentacle trimmer living on a giant octopus. Unravel dark secrets as the line between dream and reality begins to blur

Interested? Please, wishlist Octopus City Blues on Steam. Likes and channel subscriptions are also highly appreciated! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1192230/Octopus_City_Blues/
